    "description": "——时为科学世纪。<br>用53分钟就能从首都京都到达东京的全地下新干线『广重』也已经通车。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/e803b26de694b50c830829dbbc93f531.avif?t=1628842700\" width=580 height=200 /></span><br>玛艾露贝莉・赫恩。宇佐见莲子。<br><br>两人现在——<br><br>还尚未相遇。<br><br><br>～游戏概要～<br><br>这是一款以解谜为主的二次创作文字冒险游戏。<br>以上海爱丽丝幻乐团的「秘封俱乐部」系列作为题材。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/012b072c433d4e70f7be59b5af156724.avif?t=1628842700\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br>故事发生在秘封俱乐部的第一部作品《莲台野夜行～Ghostly Field Club》之前。<br>游戏开始于大学的入学仪式之后，梅莉和莲子相遇的那一刻。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/932f39ea97932a2976796f0e20c4b22e.avif?t=1628842700\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br>使用从两人对话中获得的记忆「碎片」中导出的词汇<br>最终完成『莲台野夜行』的故事，是这个游戏的目标。<br><br><br>～记忆「碎片」～<br><br>「碎片」系统灵感来源自「合资会社自行车创业」的「ANOS系统」<br>比起以前的文字冒险游戏，该系统带来了全新的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/03a7af8dcb26ebeaee3280b51023ecdc.poster.avif?t=1628842700\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/03a7af8dcb26ebeaee3280b51023ecdc.webm?t=1628842700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/03a7af8dcb26ebeaee3280b51023ecdc.mp4?t=1628842700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从故事中获得的文章「碎片」中自由选择词语<br>生成推动故事前进的「关键词」。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/a52080ecd47741e98b378b7fbbc64cfc.poster.avif?t=1628842700\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/a52080ecd47741e98b378b7fbbc64cfc.webm?t=1628842700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/a52080ecd47741e98b378b7fbbc64cfc.mp4?t=1628842700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果在剧情节点设定相应关键词，就会走上分支路线。<br>可以看到新的剧情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/f52261ba20dd0e8e5ce0b84253b7d7ea.poster.avif?t=1628842700\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/f52261ba20dd0e8e5ce0b84253b7d7ea.webm?t=1628842700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/f52261ba20dd0e8e5ce0b84253b7d7ea.mp4?t=1628842700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>因为并不能像以前的冒险游戏那样，单纯尝试每一个选项，<br>所以，只是漫不经心地阅读文章是无法通关本作的。<br><br><br><br>命运有「不同路径」，人生却没有「选项」——<br><br>秘封俱乐部的两人，能打开莲台野的入口吗……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568880/extras/fee9e983edd7f00d9d9a1ffcb9209222.avif?t=1628842700\" width=500 height=374 /></span><br><br>关于游戏过程中容易遇到困难的部分，我们制作了比游戏中的线索更循序渐进的“分阶段提示攻略”。<br>如果能作为游戏过程中的参考就太好了。<br><br>※对于想要无提示通关的人来说这是多余的帮助，请注意不要阅览。<br><br>",
